title: 2001–02 Northern Football League
text:
The 2001–02 Northern Football League season was the 104th in the history of <a href="Northern%20Football%20League">Northern Football League</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in England.
Division One.
Division One featured 18 clubs which competed in the division last season, along with three new clubs, promoted from Division Two:
Division Two.
Division Two featured 16 clubs which competed in the division last season, along with four new clubs.
